WEBVTT

00:00:00.782 --> 00:00:02.687
Zamislite da ste u Rimu

00:00:02.711 --> 00:00:05.914
i prispeli ste do Vatikanskih muzeja.

00:00:06.301 --> 00:00:09.544
Vukli ste se kroz dugačke hodnike,

00:00:09.568 --> 00:00:14.008
pored statua, fresaka
i mnogih drugih stvari.

00:00:14.380 --> 00:00:16.725
Uputili ste se ka Sikstinskoj kapeli.

00:00:16.749 --> 00:00:22.125
Konačno - dugačak hodnik,
stepenik i vrata.

00:00:22.149 --> 00:00:25.147
Nalazite se na pragu Sikstinske kapele.

00:00:25.171 --> 00:00:26.935
Pa, šta očekujete?

00:00:26.959 --> 00:00:29.483
Uzdignute zvonike? Horove anđela?

00:00:29.507 --> 00:00:31.665
Nemamo ništa od toga tamo.